data.description: Don't miss out on this one! 4.26 acres w/a total of 2577 sf of heated living space. This oasis is located at the end of a cul-de-sac with lots of privacy! The property has apple trees, a stream running along the back side and currently has 3 separate gardens.  The upper & lower levels of the home include a total of 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, laundry up AND down and a 2-car attached garage.  Additional features include hardwoods throughout the main level, workshop w/electricity, wood burning stove, 16X32 inground, saltwater pool, and an extra-large covered porch off the back for entertaining. There is an additional, attached 1 car garage with a studio apartment and 1/2 bath. The addition has a great workspace with tons of storage. Private well with water softener system.
